Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.07,0:26:07.72,Musical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}♪ Flower, flower! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.82,0:26:09.68,Musical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}♪ Tree! Tree! ♪
