Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.72,0:26:09.22,Musical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}♪ Flower, flower! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.22,0:26:10.88,Musical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}♪ Flower, flower! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.88,0:26:12.54,Musical,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}♪ Flower, flower! ♪
